Hello all!!!!

It is good to see activity again on the list! :)

I have access to the wiki site once more and so I may be doing so
pruning some time in the very near future.

Who is still active??????  Whoi wants to be active??? Everyone please
declare what characters you wish to utilize. This is the time if you
feel you want to make changes it will be easier to do so.

If you have too many characters and want to drop some feel free.

If you feel you want more, then carefully consider how many characters
you can handle AND STILL MAKE MEANINGFUL POSTS and then let me know.
:)

Some of us have a LOT of characters and I have seen a few one and two
line posts float by. Please only choose the number of characters that
you can handle and still make meaningful posts.- yeah I said it twice
:)

Also I encourage those that can to make charaters on different sides.
Our Max side is heavy with characters while the pred side is only me
and Airly. Again, this is not a requirement, it is only a suggestion.
I may be waking the unicron isde up as well, if anyone wants a
character on that side let me know.

Anyways, I look foward to responses. I will be moving characters not
claimed or discarded to the inactive parts of the list or take on
their roles myself to keep things moving, depending on the need.

To view the wiki list you can check here:
http://www.wikihost.org//w/nbwrpg_wiki/character_list

Thanks
Preston
